title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Residues & Waste From Prepared Food Inds.
description: Imports Intra Eu - Residues & Waste From Prepared Food Inds. in the United Kingdom decreased to 145.24 GBP Million in September from 166.87 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Residues & Waste From Prepared in the United Kingdom averaged 567.88 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 85253.80 GBP Million in March of 2015 and a record low of 20.61 GBP Million in May of 1999.
